org.apache.flume.instrumentation
Interface ChannelCounterMBean

All Known Implementing Classes:
ChannelCounter
public interface ChannelCounterMBean

This interface represents a channel counter mbean. Any class implementing this interface must sub-class MonitoredCounterGroup. This interface might change between minor releases. Please see ChannelCounter class.
